it's a bad idea.

40:44.543 --> 40:47.544
You never know what could
summon mr. Mordrake.

40:47.546 --> 40:50.713
Even a rehearsal
is risky business.

40:50.715 --> 40:53.383
Dot: You carnies are
so superstitious.

40:53.385 --> 40:55.051
He's a myth.

40:55.053 --> 40:56.953
I am the only myth around here.

40:58.389 --> 41:00.223
