been summoned.

47:14.933 --> 47:17.767
And now, sadly, we are here

47:17.769 --> 47:20.303
And cannot leave this place
until we have added

47:20.305 --> 47:23.773
To our coterie
of freakish companions.

47:23.775 --> 47:25.775
You say "companions."

47:25.777 --> 47:27.944
You-you mean "victims."

47:27.946 --> 47:30.613
It is not in my heart
to make you

47:30.615 --> 47:33.449
