47:51.803 --> 47:54.804
Would that it were in my
power to grant reprieve.

47:54.806 --> 47:58.474
But if the vile countenance
a-judges you a pure freak--

47:58.476 --> 48:00.810
Corrupted of flesh,
befouled of soul--

48:00.812 --> 48:02.645
