50:53.985 --> 50:56.152
Be but sworn my love.

50:56.154 --> 50:58.521
<i>Well, nobody wanted</i>
<i>to see some hairy broad</i>

50:58.523 --> 50:59.989
<i>Reciting the classics.</i>

50:59.991 --> 51:01.357
<i>They laughed all right.</i>

51:01.359 --> 51:03.993
<i>This time I wasn't</i>
<i>in on the joke.</i>

51:03.995 --> 51:05.528
<i>I was the joke.</i>

51:05.530 --> 51:07.897
How dreadful for you.

51:09.032 --> 51:11.400
(indistinct whispering)

51:13.170 --> 51:15.704
What's it saying?

51:15.706 --> 51:20.176
It knows you have a deeper pain.

51:20.178 --> 51:22.244
A darker shame?

51:26.683 --> 51:29.018
Yes.

51:29.020 --> 51:32.855
When you returned
to the states,

51:32.857 --> 51:35.925
What happened?

51:39.696 --> 51:42.264
We were penniless.

51:46.036 --> 51:48.437
I was carrying dell's child.

51:50.874 --> 51:54.376
We couldn't find carny work.

51:54.378 --> 51:58.114
And I couldn't do my act--
not in that condition.

52:02.719 --> 52:05.788
So, dell arranged...

52:08.558 --> 52:11.260
...A different kind
of command performance.

52:11.262 --> 52:13.262
Dell: <i>Grab some peanuts</i>
<i>on your way in, sir.</i>

52:13.264 --> 52:15.064
Thank you so much.

52:15.066 --> 52:16.232
Step right up, folks.

52:16.234 --> 52:18.067
It's the marvel of the century.

52:18.069 --> 52:19.768
A live freak birth.

52:19.770 --> 52:22.071
Something like you've
never seen before.

52:22.073 --> 52:24.907
Right before your very eyes,
a live freak birth.

52:24.909 --> 52:26.075
Right this way, sir!

52:26.077 --> 52:28.777
Right before
your very eyes, folks!

